Happy Workout Wednesday! Here is an awesome Kettlebell workout that you can do anywhere! 
1. Single-Leg Deadlift + Upright Row
2.Single-Leg & Single Shoulder Kettlebell Press
3. Kettlebell Swings
4. One-legged Kettlebell Row
5. Reverse Lunge + Pass Through
6. Squat Pulses + Jump

If you are looking to tone, move from one exercise to the next with little to no rest. After completing one full circuit, jump rope for one minute, rest and then repeat circuit for 3-4 times.

If you are looking to strengthen or have a tough time putting on muscle do each move back to back with at least 30-45 seconds rest in between sets. Repeat the move 3-4 times before moving onto the next. Finish with 5 minutes of jumping rope!
